summary: Defines a collection of Django model classes used in test suites to exercise many‑to‑many relationships, including custom through models, self‑referencing many‑to‑many links, and related entities such as Person, Group, Event, Employee, and Membership.
business_intent: Provide test data structures that enable verification of ORM behavior for many‑to‑many relationships with custom through tables and self‑referencing associations.
